Class Resource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.liferay.apio.architect.resource.Resource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Resource.GenericParent, Resource.Item, Resource.Nested, Resource.Paged

    @ProviderType
public class Resource
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of this class represent an API resource.

    Only three implementations are allowed: Resource.Item, Resource.Paged and Resource.Nested.

    This class should never be directly instantiated. Use one of its descendants static methods (Resource.Paged.of(java.lang.String), Resource.Item.of(java.lang.String) and Resource.Nested.of(com.liferay.apio.architect.resource.Resource.Item, java.lang.String)) instead.

    See Also:
    Resource.Item, Resource.Paged, Resource.Nested
